data.description: Well Cared for Move-In Ready Personal Residence or Investment Property! Neutral Decor w/Fresh Neutral Paint & Floors! MAIN LEVEL: 1.5 Story Entry w/Inviting Wood Floor. Kitchen: Vaulted Ceiling w/Beautiful Tall Abundant Cabinets, Tile Backsplash, Black Appliances, Wonderfully Convenient Wood Floor, Eat In Area w/Lots of Natural light. Living Room: Abundant Natural Light, Vaulted Ceiling, Sliding door to Nice Back-yard Deck overlooking the Common Area. 3 Bedrooms on Main w/Primary En-Suite. LOWER LEVEL: Rec-Room w/Daylight Window & Access to 2-Car Garage w/Work Room. Laundry Area w/Washer & Dryer ALL Included! EXTERIOR: Vinyl Siding, Fenced Back-Yard w/Nice Deck & Deep Driveway. UTILITY AVGS: OPPD: $100 / MUD: $136   SCHOOL DISTRICT: Omaha Public Schools  CLOSE TO: Schools, Shopping, Restaurants, Golf, Parks, Recreation, 27 Min to Offutt AFB.  *** 1 YEAR ServiceOne Home Warranty *** w/No Exclusions will transfer to Buyer at Close! Offers accepted through 10 PM Sunday, 7 APRIL 2024.
